@startuml Sequence_Candidate_CV
title Ứng Viên - Quản Lý CV (Module C)

actor Candidate as "👤 Ứng viên"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant CVService as "CV\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== Danh Sách CV ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "CV của tôi"
FrontEnd -> CVService: GET /api/cvs?page=0&size=10
CVService -> Database: Query ho_so_cv (candidateId)
Database --> CVService: Return list
CVService --> FrontEnd: CV list
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Hiển thị danh sách CV

== Tạo CV Mới ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Tạo CV"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Show CV form
Candidate -> FrontEnd: Nhập: tên CV, mô tả
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Validate input
FrontEnd -> CVService: POST /api/cvs\n(tenCv, moTa)
CVService -> Database: Create ho_so_cv
Database --> CVService: Return cvId
CVService --> FrontEnd: CV created
FrontEnd --> Candidate: ✅ Tạo CV thành công

== Xem Chi Tiết CV ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Xem"
FrontEnd -> CVService: GET /api/cvs/{cvId}
CVService -> Database: Get ho_so_cv + chi_tiet + skills
Database --> CVService: Return full CV data
CVService --> FrontEnd: CV details
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Hiển thị CV

== Thêm Kinh Nghiệm & Học Vấn ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Thêm kinh nghiệm"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Show form
Candidate -> FrontEnd: Nhập: công ty, vị trí, thời gian
FrontEnd -> CVService: POST /api/cvs/{cvId}/hoc-van-kn\n(loai=KINH_NGHIEM, ...)
CVService -> Database: Create chi_tiet_cv
Database --> CVService: OK
CVService --> FrontEnd: Experience added
FrontEnd --> Candidate: ✅ Thêm kinh nghiệm

== Thêm Kỹ Năng ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Thêm kỹ năng"
FrontEnd -> CVService: GET /api/system-skills
CVService -> Database: Get all system skills
Database --> CVService: Return skills list
CVService --> FrontEnd: Skills list
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Show skills dropdown

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Chọn kỹ năng & mức độ
FrontEnd -> CVService: POST /api/cvs/{cvId}/skills\n(skillId, thanhThaoDo)
CVService -> Database: Create ct_ky_nang_hs
Database --> CVService: OK
CVService --> FrontEnd: Skill added
FrontEnd --> Candidate: ✅ Thêm kỹ năng

== Upload PDF CV ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Upload PDF"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Show file picker
Candidate -> FrontEnd: Select PDF file
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Validate file (PDF only)
FrontEnd -> CVService: POST /api/cvs/{cvId}/upload-file\n(file.pdf)
CVService -> CVService: Store file
CVService -> Database: Update fileCvUrl
Database --> CVService: OK
CVService --> FrontEnd: File uploaded
FrontEnd --> Candidate: ✅ Upload xong

== Cập Nhật CV ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Sửa"
FrontEnd -> CVService: PUT /api/cvs/{cvId}\n(tenCv, moTa)
CVService -> Database: Update ho_so_cv
Database --> CVService: OK
CVService --> FrontEnd: CV updated
FrontEnd --> Candidate: ✅ CV cập nhật

== Xóa CV ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Xóa"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Confirm dialog
Candidate -> FrontEnd: Xác nhận xóa
FrontEnd -> CVService: DELETE /api/cvs/{cvId}
CVService -> Database: Delete ho_so_cv & chi_tiet
Database --> CVService: OK
CVService --> FrontEnd: CV deleted
FrontEnd --> Candidate: ✅ Xóa thành công

== Đặt CV Mặc Định ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Đặt làm mặc định"
FrontEnd -> CVService: PUT /api/cvs/{cvId}/default
CVService -> Database: Update isDefault flag
Database --> CVService: OK
CVService --> FrontEnd: Default set
FrontEnd --> Candidate: ✅ Đặt làm mặc định

@enduml
